messages.text: did you see the news?
The world's freaking out.
all over - floods in Japan, drought in Russia, dead penguins in Antarctica -
We've been lucky. Maybe the worse is over.
i don't know - i feel the hammer's gonna come down real hard real soon
Where's that faith you were talking about?
still got it - holding onto it - but it ain't easy
Wait - Do you hear that?
yeah - a loud weird siren
Shit - now what...?
Gonna check the news again...
Eva, it's another hurricane warning. You better stay inside.
Eva...?
EVA?!
a little bit later
can't chat long my dad is gonna stick us in his underground shelter behind the house
only got a couple minutes before i'm locked up like a prisoner
Can't you run away?
no he's got the perimeter wired w/ motion sensors
Can you get to the controls?
it's in the electric room - but he's in there packing up his guns
Does the room have a phone?
no, the nearest phone's upstairs - why?
He's gonna get a call from a TV station saying they want to do a story on him.
I'll keep him on long enough for you to disable the alarms.
you are so sneaky! 😈
that's why i love u!!
a little bit later
aaron it's no use -
he came back and won't let me out of his sight
he's forcing me underground
don't forget our promise -
we won't let anyone stop us from being together
luv u 4ever
4ever!!
that night
took me all nite to get a connection
Eva! You ok?
tired, frustrated, bored - no cell coverage down here
just a bunch of canned peaches and dried meat
How did you get a signal?
lifted some shit from the hardware store - wires, tape...
connected phone to the tv antenna - instant extended coverage
You robbed the store?
wasn't thinking just grabbing - like impulse buying but without the buying
i call it impulse looting
You rock!
wanna save battery till we figure out what to do next
Were you able to turn off the outside motion alarms?
yeah, but what good does that do us now?
I can come there and get you! While they're sleeping!
but i can't open the hatch from the inside without the code
& dad didn't care to share
I guess you need the code to open it from the outside too.
roger that
ok...thinking...
Got it!
What?
I have an infrared camera app on my phone.
I'll scan the keypad and see which buttons he pressed.
u r awesome!!!
thanks
what r u waiting for? come rescue me!!!
a little bit later
finally back online
Been trying to send you messages for hours!
I got to your bunker at 2am - but there was someone outside the hatch.
yup - white haired guy in a suit
Who's he?
my uncle Barry - came to join our happy family
I saw him enter, so I didn't want to risk coming inside.
yeah...getting crowded in here
But I got good news...
i could use it
I saw him punch in the access code:
my hero! i'm coming out now - where r u?
At a friend's house - 10 minutes away
ok - u better be here to get me
If I'm lying I'm dying...
a little bit later
Eva, I'm here.
Come out!
a little bit later
i fucked up
What is it?
i made too much noise at the hatch
they caught me & dragged me back in
they also changed the code
Shit!!
now they have me on kitchen detail...
bad fucking luck...
i'm sorry - why r we so doomed?
Never surrender!
why not? everything's gone to shit
I'll camp outside until you escape.
what about your folks? where r they?
Packing up all our stuff. Planning to move next week.
They only know that I'm staying with a friend.
and when they call u back?
Let's worry about that later.
For now we need another plan.
what if we both kill ourselves?
You don't mean that.
i feel like it. i wanna die -
I won't let you.
but the world is ending
We're both alive. And as long as we still breathe, and have our love -
we have it better than the rest of the world.
i guess...
Besides, you haven't heard my song yet.
true dat...
that's the reason i need to live
Like you said - all we need is us.
still have to stop my folks from keeping us apart...
Hey! I got it!
yes???
You guys must have a supply of medicine stashed there, right?
what? you want me to overdose my family?
no -
just put them to sleep for a while...
Click below to see what happens next...
